description:
A full-featured Swiss Army Knife for your brain.

The full-featured mind mapping and brainstorming app. Like a Swiss Army Knife, Xmind offers a complete toolset for thinking and creativity.
Important Updates
1. Planned Task – Clearer task details and progress tracking, making updates easy to follow;
2. Kazakh Language Support – Kazakh has been added as an interface language, enabling smooth thinking and borderless expression.
Improvements
1. Added a new topic shape – Card;
2. Floating topics now support freely adjusting the layer order;
3. Optimized some UI designs and text;
4. Optimized the display logic of Team on the Home;
5. Improved date selection logic in Planned Task;
6. Theme Editor now support selecting Grid structure;
7. Password visibility toggle is now supported in link sharing and file encryption;
8. Fixed collaboration issues caused by editing a planned task;
9. Fixed an issue where inserting Markers might cause the canvas to freeze;
10. Fixed an issue where the border opacity setting was not working in Grid structure;
11. Fixed an issue where clicking Relationship in the search panel did not trigger a jump;
12. Fixed an issue where inserting attachments larger than 20MB in topics might cause an error;
13. Fixed an issue where the app might crash after startup;
14. Fixed some other known issues.
